title: mzcli - derbybackup - MediationZone Documentation 9.4 - InfoZone
text: Usage derbybackup <directory> This command performs a Derby database online backup, where the target directory, that is the value of <directory>, refers to the remote directory on the platform host. Return Codes The different return codes for the derbybackup command are listed below: Code Description Code Description 0 Will be returned if the command was successful or unsuccessful. 1 Will be returned if the argument count is incorrect.
